$to   = Environment::LOCAL;

if (!in_array($from, Environment::cases(), true)) {
    WP_CLI::error("Invalid environment");
}
```

**Pros:** Type-safe, self-documenting, easy to autocomplete.  
**Cons:** Requires PHP 8.1+.

