### 3\. Map to additional info

If you also need URLs, DB names, or directories:

```
$env_config = [
    Environment::LOCAL => [
        'db'   => 'local_db',
        'url'  => 'https://local.example.com',
        'root' => '/var/www/local',
    ],
    Environment::STAGING => [
        'db'   => 'staging_db',
