To fully clarify the host vs Docker distinction, I‚Äôd suggest a **small tweak**:

```
final class MigrationWorkspace {

    public function __construct(
        public readonly string $base_dir, 
        public readonly ?string $runner_base_dir = null, // optional container path
    ) { }

    // PHP / host paths
    public function temp_dir(): string {
        return $this->base_dir . '/tmp';
    }

    public function artifacts_dir(): string {
        return $this->base_dir . '/artifacts';        
    }

    public function logs_dir(): string {
        return $this->base_dir . '/logs';
    }

    // container paths for Docker/CLI runners
    public function runner_temp_dir(): string {
        return $this->runner_base_dir
            ? $this->runner_base_dir . '/tmp'
            : $this->temp_dir();
    }

    public function runner_artifacts_dir(): string {
        return $this->runner_base_dir
            ? $this->runner_base_dir . '/artifacts'
            : $this->artifacts_dir();
    }
}
```

