    protected array $args = [];
}

final class WpCliCommand extends CliCommand {
    public function __construct(public string $target_url, string $description, array $args = []) {
        $this->args = $args;
        $this->args[] = '--url=' . $target_url;
    }
}
```

This works, but exposes the property to subclasses (sometimes okay).

* * *

