### Step 2 ‚ÄĒ Update RunnerFactory::make()

Currently, you‚Äôre passing `env_type` and then fetching `$this->envs[$env_type->name]` to get some mutable `DomainEnvironment`. The trick is **to always clone/derive it instead of using the original**:

```
public function make(
    string $service,
    RunnerMode $mode,
    ArtifactEnv $env_type,
    DryRunPolicy $policy,
): CommandRunner
{
    $this->logger->debug("Creating runner for service $service RunnerMode: $mode->name EnvType: $env_type->name");

    $executor = ($this->dry_run && $policy === DryRunPolicy::SKIP_EXECUTION)
        ? new DryRunExecutor($this->logger)
        : new ProcessExecutor($this->logger);

    // immutable copy of the environment for this runner
    $original_env = $this->envs[$env_type->name];
    $runner_env = new DomainEnvironment(
        db_user: $original_env->db_user,
        db_password: $original_env->db_password,
        db_name: $original_env->db_name,
        host: $original_env->host,
        port: $original_env->port,
    );

    // Optionally, override per runner
    // e.g., if RUNNER_MODE = EXEC and you need temporary user
    if ($service === 'db' && $mode === RunnerMode::EXEC) {
        $runner_env = $runner_env->withUser($original_env->db_user); // example
    }

    // create docker context
    $docker = $this->docker_map[$env_type->name]();

    return match($mode) {
        RunnerMode::RUN =>
            new DockerRunRunner(
                executor: $executor,
                docker: $docker,
                service: $service,
                env: $runner_env,  // <-- inject immutable copy
                logger: $this->logger,
            ),
        RunnerMode::EXEC =>
            new DockerExecRunner(
                executor: $executor,
                docker: $docker,
                service: $service,
                workspace: $this->workspace,
                env: $runner_env, // <-- inject immutable copy
                logger: $this->logger,
            ),
        default => throw new \LogicException(
            "No RunnerMode definition for '{$mode}' in the RunnerFactory"
        ),
    };
}
```

